  section.slide
    h1 Data Driven Documents

  section.slide
    h2 Why should we care?
    p Some very cool visualizations:
    ul
      li.slide: a(target="_blank", href="http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2012/11/02/us/politics/paths-to-the-white-house.html?_r=0") 512 Paths
