    h1 Explanatory vs. Exploratory

  sections.slide
    h2 What D3 is NOT good for
    ul
      li.slide Basic plots that you can make in one line with matplotlib
      li.slide Supporting older browsers
      li.slide Data secrecy

  section.slide
    h2 What D3 is really GREAT for
    ul
      li.slide Visualizing <a href="http://nickqizhu.github.io/dc.js/" target="_blank">multi-dimensional data</a>
      li.slide Interactivity
      li.slide Geographical data

